channel.title: What the fuck happened today?
channel.description:
I went to a computer chop-shop to get a new HDD for my busted computer. So I ask the manager if he had any, and he said he only had an 80gig when I was looking for 500gigs. I asked him if there was any way he could try and pull some strings to get me one, and he said "I'll check some stores, give me a minute".
So after waiting about thirty minutes, he came back and told me that the Computer Junkies down the street from his shop has some. I asked if he was speaking to the manager of that Computer Junkies, and he said yes.
The Computer Junkies down the street is abandoned and has been abandoned for three years.
WHO WAS PHONE?
